{
  "stem": "6277.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He offered him a job with the Germans, to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he went to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because everybody, if you are not working, you cannot go in the street.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You cannot get your piece of bread, even, to buy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So he went to work, and mother would go to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I would stay home with my sister and brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No school, no school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After a month or less, I think it was in the end of July, there were a-- there was a decree to-- we had to register.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the Jewish people had to go in some special place and register.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they gave you a piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you had to wear a Star of David.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You didn't have the right to go on the sidewalks, only on the road, as a horse.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You didn't have the right to buy merchandise in the stores, or food, even.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it went on till a few months, with such a situation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody knew what will happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But people are always hopeful, though, that this is-- this will remain with them in such a way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in September, we were told that everybody has to move to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The ghetto was organized in the suburb of Riga, in a very poor neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we are told we have to exchange our apartments for the apartments there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We tried to find an apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the territory where we lived, about 15,000 or 20,000 people, they have to move more than 30,000.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally we found-- we gave two apartments.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our friend, what lived in the same house, two families, her husband was taken in the first days, so she was with two children.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
